description:
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will contribute to a Materials Management service delivery and associated stock control processes at Goole and District Hospital (GDH) in support of operational managers within departments ensuring that stock is maintained at optimum levels and that the levels are reviewed and adjusted in accordance with fluctuating demand. The post holder will liaise with on-site Materials Management officers at GDH and colleagues operating within the Receipt and Distribution Centre. They will also link with members of the Strategic Procurement Team, Purchasing Team and the Materials Management Teams based at the other Trust sites at Scunthorpe and Grimsby. Working within the Materials Management team the post holder shall share with and identify solutions when required to ensure continuity of the service provision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will assist the Materials Management Supervisor with the provision of the Materials Management and Receipt &amp; Distribution service across GDH and in conjunction with the Supervisor contribute to the development of systems and processes to ensure standardisation and effective work methods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder is also a key contact point for external users of the system for any queries or system change requests in respect of materials management and stock control.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be required to actively support any cost control initiatives undertaken by the Trust Strategic Procurement team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alan Cooper, Materials Management Supervisor&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address alan.cooper4@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 03033 304138&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
